{"tid":913142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老細睇我Whatsapp上線時間 問我點解仲未訓 ...","createTime":"2018-11-23T07:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T08:08:28.000Z","uid":71398,"like":1718,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f402669328a58d3cfc044695f9a30cb0512701","tid":913142,"uid":71398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"話說小弟轉左份新工<br />\n職位都唔細<br />\n講真 如非必要的話 我係唔會係Whatsapp講公事<br />\n早幾日 因為工作原故要 Whatsapp 問老細野 比佢知道左我 Whatsapp 個電話 no. (我入職時唔係填呢個)<br />\n今朝一早返到公司 佢冇啦啦叫我入房<br />\n屌我心諗乜撚柒野事呀<br />\n原來佢叫我入房係問我 Profile Pic 入面個景係邊到 仲話影得好靚喎<br />\n我真係當堂 ke 一聲笑左出黎<br />\n屌你老味關你撚事咩 我求鳩奇答左佢就出去食埋個早晨全餐<br />\n就係岩岩 2 : 34 a.m. 左右<br />\n我老細冇啦啦 Whatsapp 我<br />\n條撚樣竟然問我點解咁夜都唔訓 第 2 朝邊有精神返工呀<br />\n嘩我屌你 你又做乜柒咁夜都唔訓呀？<br />\n我幾點訓都關撚你事？ <br />\n你係咪咁撚多事呀？<br />\n你係咪冇撚野做呀？<br />\n你係咪好撚好打呀？<br />\n我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"4cd8517c347dc14294e80f48d90cad133bc96448","tid":913142,"uid":31314,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"友善蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f59db98359e64beb44f57b919d8ff75bedc082c","tid":913142,"uid":71398,"like":4,"dislike":40,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"4cd8517c347dc14294e80f48d90cad133bc96448","tid":913142,"uid":31314,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"友善蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"終於有人叫岩我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d62a53eb2bbdd8980bd292bbef45d13b29298fc","tid":913142,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"豬蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607c39b21f42b9b4fbdd73c27e26354f01fad531","tid":913142,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f59db98359e64beb44f57b919d8ff75bedc082c","tid":913142,"uid":71398,"li